				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1972035/laughter#post-2679019</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 28 Oct 2016 16:34:19 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Genshed</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2643500</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really enjoyed this. The character's pain was depicted with compassion. It made me think of how tragic so many humanoid SCPs are, and how so much of the Foundation's work depends on consciously disregarding that.</p> 
				 	]]>
